/*
  Description:
    1. Decode sEMG signals sent from ESP32 Devkit v1
    2. Perform sEMG preprocessing and run model inference
    3. Control Bionic Arm
  Date: Summer 2022

  Device: Sony Spresense Main + Extension Board

  Pins needed:
  - RX -> ESP32 TX2
  - GND -> ESP32 GND
*/

